OL,7,GYou get what you pay for. It's an old
OL,8,Gcliche but it applies to the BBC's
OL,9,Gfinancial situation.
OL,11,FThe announcement concerning the
OL,12,Ffuture of Newsnight highlights the
OL,13,FBBC's financial problems.
OL,15,FI have discussed Newsnight's
OL,16,Fdeclining audience before and whether
OL,17,Fit had a future in its traditional
OL,18,Fform.
