OL,3,CDedicated Newsnight in-depth
OL,4,Cjournalism: luxury BBC can no longer
OL,5,Cafford
OL,7,FBut nobody who cares about serious
OL,8,Fjournalism or public service
OL,9,Fbroadcasting can deny the vital
OL,10,Fimportance of in-depth reporting and
OL,11,Fanalysis.
OL,13,FThe question is whether the way that
OL,14,Fjournalism was structured made
OL,15,Feconomic sense.
OL,17,FNewsnight has its own dedicated and
OL,18,Frespected team of reporters.
