OL,3,CDedicated Newsnight in-depth
OL,4,Cjournalism: luxury BBC can no longer
OL,5,Cafford
OL,7,FIt is also vitally important to
OL,8,Fretain the skills of the individuals.
OL,9,FAny compulsory redundancies would be
OL,10,Ffiercely opposed by the NUJ and would
OL,11,Fbe likely to lead to industrial
OL,12,Faction.
OL,14,FBut sadly allowing one programme
OL,15,Falone such a large, dedicated team
OL,16,F(with work which rarely featured on
OL,17,Fother linear outlets despite its
OL,18,Fquality) is a luxury the BBC cannot
OL,19,Fafford just now with the very real
OL,20,Fsqueeze on its income.
