OL,3,CDedicated Newsnight in-depth
OL,4,Cjournalism: luxury BBC can no longer
OL,5,Cafford
OL,7,FUltimately it is an impossible circle
OL,8,Fto square. The very point of a
OL,9,Fpublicly funded broadcaster is that
OL,10,Fit does important things which may
OL,11,Fnot make commercial sense.
OL,13,FThe BBC needs more money if it is to
OL,14,Fsurvive in its current form.
OL,16,FThere needs to be a proper public
OL,17,Fdebate ahead of the general election.
