OL,3,CDedicated Newsnight in-depth
OL,4,Cjournalism: luxury BBC can no longer
OL,5,Cafford
OL,7,FAre there realistic alternatives to
OL,8,Fthe licence fee as a form of direct
OL,9,Fpublic funding? The suggestion of a
OL,10,F"household charge" added to council
OL,11,Ftax bills at a level which varies
OL,12,Faccording to council tax bands is
OL,13,Fcertainly interesting.
OL,15,FOr is a flat rate charge still the
OL,16,Fleast worst option? And if so what
OL,17,Fshould the charge be?
OL,19,FThere would seem to be a high chance
OL,20,Fat present of a Labour government
OL,21,Fafter the next election. What will be
OL,22,Fin their manifesto?
