OL,4,Cjournalism: luxury BBC can no longer
OL,5,Cafford
OL,7,FWill they keep the licence fee?
OL,8,FCommit to a one-off restorative rise?
OL,9,FThen annual rises in line with
OL,10,Finflation?
OL,12,FOr would this simply give political
OL,13,Fopponents an opportunity to say a
OL,14,FLabour government would cost voters
OL,15,Fmoney?
OL,17,FIt's not an easy time for all of us
OL,18,Fwho care about public service
OL,19,Fbroadcasting.
OL,21,FIt must be efficiently run and
OL,22,Fprovide best value for money.
